George Grizzard https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Grizzard 0 George Cooper Grizzard, Jr. (April 1, 1928 – October 2, 2007) was an American Emmy Award- and Tony Award-winning actor of film, stage, and television. He appeared in more than 40 films, dozens of television programs, and a number of Broadway plays. George_Cooper_Grizzard , Jr .
